Deck I put together for a local tournament, still can't decide if it's good or not, super poly seemed like a good addition but the deck and extra deck become cramped with extra additions. I didn't even have space to put Predaplant Dragostapelia inside, but didn't want to get rid of Chain Coils since it has served me well several times. Arguably, I could've gotten rid of 3rd Sera, but oh well. 

Super Poly did a lot of work, but it's 50/50 that it leaves me without follow-up plays, which really sucked.

I'll be happy to answer questions about the deck and please do give any suggestions.
